Attack of the Warzone Water Bottles

by Benjamin Preston | May 16, 2011

Years ago, when I attended Marine Corps recruit training at Parris Island, South Carolina, we had it drummed into our heads right away to constantly drink water. “Get a canteen into your suck, yoohoo!” the drill instructors would scream at regular intervals.
